{"tid":1422803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無交通燈好危險！大家小心！","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:51:11.000Z","uid":300774,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e980afdc3e10f03775ecc77e097d57e0fcdcb371","tid":1422803,"uid":300774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">明白大家有提出訴求及示威的權利，但是希望各位可以體諒一下市民的人生安全，不要破壞交通燈好嗎？現在大家都冒著危險過馬路和開車，整個銅鑼灣都找不到一盞運作正常的🚥 司機如果看不到有人直駛出去就會有人受傷甚至失去生命。希望各位享有自由的同時亦要顧及大家香港人的安全與權益，謝謝🙏</span>"},{"pid":"e513608420fa93804c40020a9bcda1407a61910a","tid":1422803,"uid":284104,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"唔識揸車/淘寶牌先會覺得有問題囉"},{"pid":"6019a78bb63feab15db054aa19df7a9be6244023","tid":1422803,"uid":300774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e513608420fa93804c40020a9bcda1407a61910a","tid":1422803,"uid":284104,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"唔識揸車/淘寶牌先會覺得有問題囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"公公婆婆行得慢，眼又睇得唔清楚，係咪要顧及吖？"},{"pid":"2125017dbd63dd9066e09e03c9728f5e4872c5d5","tid":1422803,"uid":274513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e513608420fa93804c40020a9bcda1407a61910a","tid":1422803,"uid":284104,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"唔識揸車/淘寶牌先會覺得有問題囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母講得出呢句野我地注定運動會失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登式既民主無人想要，因為大陸而家已經係咁"},{"pid":"c999ddfc4f0bfb12948797cc00ceb703a7c1f4ad","tid":1422803,"uid":284104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6019a78bb63feab15db054aa19df7a9be6244023","tid":1422803,"uid":300774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":